to Diversity
<div class="bbi-back">
 <div class="bbi-flex-cont">
  <p>
   Christian, ecumenical, interreligious, world-engaged, broad in thought, and welcoming to all who venture in—Union values &amp; celebrates the diversity of its students, faculty and staff.
  </p>
